tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SpeedAndLocationData (
  vehicle_id INT,
  speed DECIMAL,
  latitude DECIMAL,
  longitude DECIMAL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (vehicle_id, timestamp)
)

CREATE TABLE LocationData (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE FuelEfficiency (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    fuel_consumption FLOAT,
    efficiency_score FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE Location_Data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Fuel_Efficiency (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    fuel_level FLOAT,
    efficiency_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Vehicle_Info (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    make VARCHAR(255),
    model VARCHAR(255),
    year INT
);

CREATE TABLE VehicleInfo (
  vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  model VARCHAR(255),
  year INT,
  fuel_type VARCHAR(50)
);
